commit.message:
Improve table styling

Use Bootstrap table classes for rst tables by default.  However, add
two GLEP-specific changes:

- force `width: auto` to improve readability of tables with few columns

- force `vertical-align: middle` for cells to improve rowspans

Signed-off-by: Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
